Rogue Scholar
In a world where the Coalition States burns books and suppresses free thought,
the Rogue Scholar preserves knowledge at great personal risk. They are
self-taught intellectuals obsessed with history, science, and discovery.

Rogue Scholars begin with multiple languages and literacy skills, plus a broad
academic base. They favour Technical, Science, Medical, and Lore skill categories.

Attribute requirements: None. Any OCC-eligible race may choose Rogue Scholar.
Starting equipment: Laptop computer, collection of data discs, concealed
sidearm, scholarly clothes, and a journal.
